	  <div id="accordion">
	  <h3>1.How do I request a reservation?</h3>
	  <div>
	    <p>Have you found any interesting travel? If so, press the [Request a reservation] button at the bottom of the travel item screen. The application will go to the Roller or guide who are going to carry out the travel. You will get a response within 24 hours. Once accepted, you can proceed with the payment. Payment must be done within another 24 hours. When the payment is completed, the reservation will be confirmed. If you do not pay within 24 hours, it will be automatically canceled and will be counted on your cancel log.</p>
	  </div>
	  <h3>2.Is it possible to change a reservation?</h3>
	  <div>
	    <p>It is not possible to make changes after making a reservation request. You can cancel your existing reservation request and request a new reservation. If you cancel the reservation request before you get an accetance from a Roller or a guide, it will not be counted on cancel log.</p>
	  </div>
	  <h3>3.Do I have to pay if my reservation request isn't accepted by the roller or guide?</h3>
	  <div>
	    <p>If a roller or guide has refused or expired (ie, did not respond within 24 hours), the reservation request will be automatically canceled with expiration.</p>
	  </div>
	  <h3>4.How do I send and view messages?</h3>
	  <div>
	    <p>After making a reservation request, you can messge to your roller or guide. You can find it in the message screen through the message menu.</p>    
	  </div>
	  <h3>5.How much time does a roller or guide have to respond to my reservation request?</h3>
	  <div>
	    <p>Rollers or guides must respond to the reservation request within 24 hours of receiving the travel reservation request. If rollers or guides do not select accept / refuse within 24 hours, the reservation request will expire and will automatically be refused(canceled). </p>    
	  </div>
